Package com.eteks.sweethome3d.model Description

Describes model classes of Sweet Home 3D. This is the core package of Sweet Home 3D upon which all the other packages are dependent.

The HomeApplication abstract class is the entry point of this package, and gives access to user preferences, to the list of created homes, with their walls, furniture,... and how to read and write homes.
